            "body": "Single-purpose variables aren't the right direction. Using `vim.g` / `vim.b` for the full \"config\" of a topic (e.g. `vim.g.lsp = { inlay_hints = ..., ... }`, `vim.b.lsp = { ... }`) could be very helpful (and avoids an inner platform in every goddamn module), but requires https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/12544#issuecomment-1116794687 ... The alternative to that is to graduate these into \"real\" editor options.",
